        "description": "Assess the feasibility of leveraging machine learning (ML)-based text classification models to automatically categorize advertisers into 634 predefined categories under the _Media Radar taxonomy._\n\n**Objectives:**\n\n* Evaluate the suitability of ML-based text classification approaches for multi-class / multi-label advertiser categorization.\n* Identify data requirements and candidate models.\n* Assess data availability, quality, and labeling needs.\n* Estimate expected classification accuracy.\n\n",
