        "description": "As a regional lead, I want to be certain that the Optimal Solution can work fully and properly in my region. I will achieve this by getting a detailed report of what data is visible and used, to be compared with our own understanding of the regional data.\n\nProvide numbers based on 3 month period: 2026 Q1  \nData availability report: <custom data-type=\"smartlink\" data-id=\"id-0\">https://adgear.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/AGILE/pages/22843424830/FRITES+Data+Exploration</custom> \n\n**Analysis to be provided:**\n\n* Universe size based on user and exposure data\n* Linear vs. AVOD exposure breakdown\n* Linear apps exposure breakdown\n* HDMI device categories exposure breakdown\n* Regional brands exposure breakdown\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n\n* Every report mentioned above provided and documented\n* **Main findings summarized in a presentation**\n* Any coverage gaps documented with remediation plan\n* All issues resolved, added as tasks, or escalated as blockers\n* Report acceptance confirmation from regional lead\n\n",
